  [7]: http://i.stack.imgur.com/3Z0a5.png
  [8]: https://openjfx.io/javadoc/17/javafx.graphics/javafx/scene/Node.html
  [9]: https://www.pluralsight.com/blog/film-games/understanding-uvs-love-them-or-hate-them-theyre-essential-to-know

